marathon

Provides a defined type to install as many Marathon UI instances as necessary

Usage
-----
Note that this is a defined type, not a class. This allows multiple marathon instances to exist on one machine.

marathon::instance { 'tomcat1':
  tomcat_webapp_dir => '/var/lib/tomcat/webapps',
}

Support
-------

Please log tickets and issues at our [Projects site](https://github.com/meltwater/puppet-marathon)

Pull Requests are always welcome
